            <h3 class="h3 p-3 bg-info text-white">Filing of Forms:</h3>
            <br />
            <p class="text-justify">The company shall file with the Registrar of Companies form MGT 14.</p>
            <p class="text-justify font-weight-bold">Required Documents:</p>
            <ol style="font-size:18px;">
                <li>Notice of General Meeting</li>
                <li>Altered Memorandum of Association</li>
                <li>Extract of Special Resolution passed at the General Meeting</li>
                <li>Other requisite documents</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
